                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                      <locus from="1v"></locus>
                      <title type="complete" ref="NAR0003tables" xml:lang="en">A table in two parts,
                      arranged according to the days of the week, from Wednesday to Tuesday, giving the
                    <foreign xml:lang="gez">አበቅቴ፡</foreign>, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጥንትዮን፡</foreign>,
                    <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሠርቀ፡ ሌሊት፡</foreign>, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ፋሲካ፡</foreign>,
                  <foreign xml:lang="gez">ፍሥሕ፡</foreign>, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዕለተ፡ ፍሥሕ፡</foreign>,
                <foreign xml:lang="gez">ድራረ፡ ጾም፡</foreign>, for a complete lunar cycle of 19 years
              (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ዓውደ፡ ቀመር፡</foreign>).</title>
                      <textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
                    </msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                      <title type="complete" ref="NAR0003tables" xml:lang="en">28 tables, each comprising a
                      lunar cycle of 19 years. The headings of the columns are
                      <foreign xml:lang="gez">ታሪ<lb/>ክ፡ ዓው<lb/>ቀመ፡ ዓው<lb/>ወር፡ ልደ<lb/>አበ፡ ጳጕ<lb/>ሜን፡
                    አው<lb/>ዓመ፡ ዕጥ<lb/>ላን<lb/>ዮት፡ አበ<lb/>ቅቴ፡ መጥ<lb/>ቅዕ፡ ሠር<lb/>ሌሊ፡ ጾመ<lb/>አይ፡
                  ሠር<lb/>ሌለ፡ መጸ<lb/>ለት፡ ሠር<lb/>ሌሊ፡ ነነ<lb/>ዌ፡ በአ<lb/>ጾም፡ ፍሥ<lb/>ሕ፡ ሠር<lb/>ሌለ፡
                ፋሲ<lb/>ካ፡</foreign></title>
                      <textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
                      <note>The column headed <foreign xml:lang="gez">ታሪክ፡</foreign> contains various
                    events, the latest of which is the accession of <persName ref="PRS8344sahlaDe"></persName>,
                  <date when="1840">1840</date>.</note>
                    </msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                      <locus from="17r"></locus>
                      <title type="complete" ref="LIT4723TarikaWaldaAmid"></title>
                      <textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
                      <note>Apparentely this is an abbreviated version</note>
                      <incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#17r"></locus>በስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ መሓሪ፡ ወመስተሣህል። ንዌጥን፡ በጽሒፈ፡ መጽሐፍ፡
                        ዘይነግር፡ በቃል፡ ዓመታተ፡ ዓለም፡ ዘአስተጋብአ፡ አብ፡ ክቡር፡ ወትሩፍ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ ወልደ፡ አሚድ፡ ዘብሔረ፡ ግብጽ፡
                        ጸሎቱ፡ ወበረከ<add>ቱ፡ ይሀሉ፡ ምስለ፡ ፍቁሩ፡ ዘአምላክ፡ ዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን።</add>
                      </incipit>
                      <explicit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#19r"></locus>
                      <persName ref="PRS5616IyasuI">ኢያሱ፡</persName> ወልዱ፡
                      ዘስመ፡ መንግሥቱ፡ አድያ<sic>መ</sic>፡ ሰገድ፡ ነግሠ፡ <add>፳ወ፬ ዓመተ፡</add>
                    </explicit>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i3.1">
                      <locus from="19r"></locus>
                      <title type="complete" xml:lang="en">Section containing rules for finding
                      epact, golden numver (<foreign xml:lang="gez">መጥቅዕ፡</foreign>),
                    plinthion (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ጥንትዮን፡</foreign>), etc.</title>
                    </msItem>
                    </msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                      <locus from="24v"></locus>
                      <title type="complete" ref="LIT6043Hassab"></title>
                      <textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
                      <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        ናሁ፡ ንጽሐፍ፡ በረድኤተ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ዜና፡ አርእስተ፡ ሐሳብ፡ ዘእምፍጥረተ፡ ዓለም፡ እስከ፡ ተፍጻሜተ፡ ዓለም፡ ወነገሩኒ፡
                        በእንተ፡ ምስጢረ፡ አቅማር፡ ወግብረ፡ ዓመታት፡ ወክፍለ፡ ሰንበታት፡ ወሱባዔሆሙ፡ ወኢዮቤልዮሳት፡ ወኡደተ፡ እንድቅትዮን፡
                        ወክፍለ፡ ጳግሜን፡ ወሐሳበ፡ ፀሐይ፡ ዘይትበሀል፡ አበቅቴ፡ ፀሐይ፡ ወአበቅቴ፡ ወርኅ፡
                      </incipit>
                    </msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                      <locus from="25r"></locus>
                      <title type="incomplete" ref="LIT6042HassabaDemetros"></title>
                      <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"></gap> ንጽሕፍ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ሐሳብ፡ ዘአስተራተኦ፡ ድሜጥሮስ፡ ሊቀ፡ ጳጳሳት፡ ዘእስክንድርያ፡ ዘተሰይመ፡ በ፻ወ፹ ዓመት፡
                        እምእርገተ፡ ክርስቶስ።
                      </incipit>
                    </msItem>
